Set up the working environment:

mkdir -p ~/zerotrust-lab/{policies,scripts,logs,resources}
cd ~/zerotrust-lab
Step 2: Create Zero Trust Policy Framework
Create the policy definition file:

nano policies/access_policy.conf
Add policy definitions (students should customize):

